    {
      "start": 124.02,
      "end": 124.7,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.7,
      "end": 126.7,
      "text": "And that was just an idea"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.7,
      "end": 128.26,
      "text": "for years and years"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.26,
      "end": 128.66,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.66,
      "end": 130.34,
      "text": "She didn't know where"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.34,
      "end": 132.18,
      "text": "or what the story is"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.18,
      "end": 133.32,
      "text": "And then finally"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.32,
      "end": 134.94,
      "text": "She had this idea of"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.94,
      "end": 136.2,
      "text": "Fa-fa-"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.2,
      "end": 136.86,
      "text": "Some 이름"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.86,
      "end": 137.96,
      "text": "Faro"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.96,
      "end": 138.6,
      "text": "Faro"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.6,
      "end": 138.86,
      "text": "Faro"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.86,
      "end": 139.6,
      "text": "Foray"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.6,
      "end": 140.44,
      "text": "Ah, foray"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.44,
      "end": 140.46,
      "text": "Foray"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.46,
      "end": 146.34,
      "text": "And she actually visited this island"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.34,
      "end": 149.36,
      "text": "In 2014, 2015 for the first time"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.36,
      "end": 150.82,
      "text": "And she loved it so much"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.82,
      "end": 152.5,
      "text": "She went there every single year"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.5,
      "end": 153.88,
      "text": "For five years"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.88,
      "end": 155.7,
      "text": "And then she made this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.7,
      "end": 156.62,
      "text": "In 2021"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.62,
      "end": 158.1,
      "text": "And it was like a"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.1,
      "end": 160.02,
      "text": "Like her dream was realized"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.02,
      "end": 162.4,
      "text": "She's gonna match these two directors"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.4,
      "end": 163.38,
      "text": "With this island"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.38,
      "end": 164.88,
      "text": "And make a movie here"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.88,
      "end": 165.38,
      "text": "와"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.38,
      "end": 168.38,
      "text": "이전에 되게 모호하게 가지고 있었던"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.38,
      "end": 169.3,
      "text": "그 아이디어를"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.3,
      "end": 171.52,
      "text": "확실히 구체화시킬 수 있었던"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.52,
      "end": 172.88,
      "text": "계기가 된 장소네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.88,
      "end": 173.6,
      "text": "Exactly"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.6,
      "end": 174.14,
      "text": "와"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.14,
      "end": 175.68,
      "text": "She turned her vague idea"
