    {
      "start": 175.68,
      "end": 176.14,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.14,
      "end": 177.62,
      "text": "That idea she had for years"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.62,
      "end": 178.82,
      "text": "into reality"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.82,
      "end": 179.24,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.24,
      "end": 180.84,
      "text": "With this beautiful island"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.84,
      "end": 181.94,
      "text": "오, 그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.94,
      "end": 183.82,
      "text": "그러면 우리 같은 경우는"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.82,
      "end": 186.62,
      "text": "좀 영감을 받기에 좋은 장소 중에"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.62,
      "end": 188.76,
      "text": "Where would it be good?"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.86,
      "end": 190.38,
      "text": "Where do you get inspired, 조샘?"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.54,
      "end": 191.24,
      "text": "어디가 좋을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.24,
      "end": 193.16,
      "text": "I get inspired in the morning"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.16,
      "end": 194.5,
      "text": "The time is important"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.5,
      "end": 196.3,
      "text": "I focus more in the morning"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.3,
      "end": 198.14,
      "text": "So when the kids are sleeping"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.14,
      "end": 198.6,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.6,
      "end": 199.7,
      "text": "And I have coffee"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.7,
      "end": 201.96,
      "text": "And I'm just sitting right there"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.96,
      "end": 202.52,
      "text": "on the couch"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.52,
      "end": 203.86,
      "text": "It's very quiet"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.86,
      "end": 204.5,
      "text": "At home"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.5,
      "end": 204.88,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.88,
      "end": 205.8,
      "text": "그렇구나"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.8,
      "end": 207.2,
      "text": "Also after I go for a run"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.2,
      "end": 207.9,
      "text": "A long run"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.9,
      "end": 209.46,
      "text": "And I get the endorphins going"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.46,
      "end": 209.78,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.78,
      "end": 211.3,
      "text": "Then I get these crazy ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.3,
      "end": 211.78,
      "text": "Here"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.78,
      "end": 212.5,
      "text": "Some are good"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.5,
      "end": 213.48,
      "text": "Some are just crazy"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.48,
      "end": 215.0,
      "text": "But I get lots of ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.0,
      "end": 216.74,
      "text": "아, 굉장히 천재적인데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.74,
      "end": 218.82,
      "text": "Crazy idea에서 모든 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.82,
      "end": 219.8,
      "text": "시작되는 거 아니겠습니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.9,
      "end": 220.56,
      "text": "Crazy ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.56,
      "end": 220.84,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.84,
      "end": 222.3,
      "text": "Crazy ideas can be good ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.3,
      "end": 223.8,
      "text": "They can be great ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.8,
      "end": 224.18,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.18,
      "end": 226.08,
      "text": "저는 집에서는 좋은 영감이"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.08,
      "end": 227.94,
      "text": "막 샘솟는 편은 아닌 것 같고"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.94,
      "end": 228.48,
      "text": "아하"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.48,
      "end": 228.92,
      "text": "그냥"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.92,
      "end": 231.84,
      "text": "When I go to a new cafe"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.84,
      "end": 232.42,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.42,
      "end": 233.12,
      "text": "이럴 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.12,
      "end": 234.14,
      "text": "I get inspired"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.14,
      "end": 235.88,
      "text": "Do you keep switching cafes?"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.14,
      "end": 236.48,
      "text": "음"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.48,
      "end": 238.48,
      "text": "It depends"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.48,
      "end": 238.9,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.9,
      "end": 240.12,
      "text": "근데 그거 뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.12,
      "end": 240.92,
      "text": "맞긴 맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.92,
      "end": 241.44,
      "text": "네 맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.44,
      "end": 242.26,
      "text": "한 장소 많이 쓰면"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.26,
      "end": 243.56,
      "text": "좀 한정적이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.56,
      "end": 245.32,
      "text": "You need to change your surroundings"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.32,
      "end": 245.8,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.8,
      "end": 247.34,
      "text": "모던한 카페도 가보고"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.34,
      "end": 249.76,
      "text": "약간 고풍스러운 카페도 찾아가 보고"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.76,
      "end": 251.96,
      "text": "이러면서 영감을 얻는 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.96,
      "end": 253.24,
      "text": "I can recommend a few cafes"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.24,
      "end": 255.62,
      "text": "We just went to in the past few days"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.62,
      "end": 255.98,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.98,
      "end": 256.66,
      "text": "파주"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.66,
      "end": 257.0,
      "text": "네"
    },
